import React from 'react'; const Trade = props => { const { trade } = props; /* buyDate, sellDate, buyPrice: myBag["buy-price"], sellPrice, numShares, profitPercent: +percentChange-1, profitUSD, candleLength, indicatorAtSell: curIndicatorValue, indicatorAtBuy: myBag["indicator-at-buy"] */ return ( <>
Purchase date:
{trade.buyDate}
Sell date:
{trade.sellDate}
Purchase price:
{trade.buyPrice}
Sell price:
{trade.sellPrice}
Number of shares:
{trade.numShares.toFixed(2)}
Profit Percent:
{trade.profitPercent>0?"+":"-"}{(trade.profitPercent*100).toFixed(2)}% ({trade.profitUSD})
) } export default Trade;
